:"Ran successful peach farm after agricultural college","body":"Lockwood and Lewis attended both Storrs and Amherst Agricultural Colleges and then co-owned Blythefield Farm in Norwalk, running a successful commercial peach operation — an unusual choice for a Vassar-educated sportswoman of her era. She returned east regularly for Vassar reunions throughout her long California years."}],"quotes":[],"sources":[{"label":"Obituary — Julia Belden Lockwood","url":"https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/115826570/julia_belden-lockwood"}],"research_sources":[],"documents":[],"slug":"julia-lockwood-1881"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}